1 wate rcraft or trailer towed from the self-service storage facility.
2 If the vehicle, watercraft or trailer is towed from the self-service
3 storage facility, the facility owner shall not be liable for the
4 vehicle, watercraft or trailer or for any damages to the vehicle,
5 watercraft or trailer once the towing company takes possession of
6 the property.
7 F. If within thirty (30) days of the delivery of a written
8 rental agreement from the owner to the occupant by hand delivery,
9 first-class mail, or, if mutually agreed between the owner and
10 occupant in the rental agreement or in an addendum to the rental
11 agreement, by electronic mail, the occupant fails to sign such
12 rental agreement, the occupant's payment of rent or continued use of
13 the storage space shall be deemed an acceptance of the rental
14 agreement and such rental agreement shall be enforceable against the
15 occupant as if it had been signed by the occupant.
